1:32:21.453 --> 1:32:25.790
Oh, this is you. Look, it has your name
and "The third grade" written on its butt.

1:32:27.668 --> 1:32:30.253
- Do you remember that?
- I remember when I made this.

1:32:30.337 --> 1:32:31.337
Yeah.

1:32:33.173 --> 1:32:34.674
- Hey, Dad, are you okay?
- Yeah.

1:32:34.758 --> 1:32:36.676
