1:32:41.849 --> 1:32:46.227
- Yeah, that's a big bird. You better cook it properly.
- Don't worry.

1:32:46.311 --> 1:32:49.313
- J ust check the leg, Dad, just to make sure.
- I will, I will.

1:32:49.398 --> 1:32:52.024
