at least another 30 minutes.

1:32:52.109 --> 1:32:55.111
Yeah. There's something I need to tell
all ofyou about your mother.

1:32:55.195 --> 1:32:57.738
As much as I loved her,
and as good a cook as she was...

1:32:57.823 --> 1:33:01.451
in all the 41 years we'd been married,
she always overcooked the turkey.

1:33:01.535 --> 1:33:06.080
Every single year.
I just never had the heart to tell her.

1:33:07.166 --> 1:33:10.460
All right. Perfect.

1:33:27.102 --> 1:33:29.103
There we go.

1:33:30.647 --> 1:33:32.732
Yeah, that would be great. Thanks.

1:33:32.816 --> 1:33:36.486
Perfect. Oh, yeah. Good boy.

1:33:41.200 --> 1:33:43.159
Okay, that's hot.

1:33:44.870 --> 1:33:47.538
Your family is making its way
in the world...

1:33:47.623 --> 1:33:51.042
